title: (Thurs Part 1) Bobby Feud: Things Americans Would Spend Their Lottery On + Caller Tyler The Pilot Answers All Our Questions About Airplanes
itunes:title: (Thurs Part 1) Bobby Feud: Things Americans Would Spend Their Lottery On + Caller Tyler The Pilot Answers All Our Questions About Airplanes
description:
We play a round of the Bobby Feud where we try to name the Top 10 things people would spend their money on if they won the lottery. Listener Tyler the Pilot calls in and answers all of our questions about airplanes and flight safety. What really happens if a passenger gets unruly? Are we really safe during turbulence?

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
